<div class="small-12 large-9 columns withdraw-credit">
    <div class="explainer">
        <h1>Withdraw credit</h1>
        <p>To request a withdrawal of your Kiva credit balance, enter the amount in US dollars that you'd like to have withdrawn into your PayPal account. Withdrawals typically take 1-2 weeks to be processed after being requested.</p>
    </div>
    <!-- This is where the rest of the content goes -->
    <div class="statistic-display">
        <div>
            <span class="statistic kiva-green">{{availableKivaCredit}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="statistic-label">Available Kiva credit</div>
    </div>
    <div class="row bottom-rule">&nbsp;</div>
    <form data-abide class="large-6">
        <div class="amount-to-withdraw-field small-6">
            <label>Amount to withdraw
                <input type="text" required pattern="^[$][0-9]{1,3}(?:,?[0-9]{3})*(?:\.[0-9]{2})?$" placeholder="$ USD">
            </label>
            <small class="error">Amount to withdraw must be a valid amount.</small>
        </div>
        <div class="paypal-email-field">
            <label>Your PayPal account email
                <input type="email" id="paypal-email" required>
            </label>
            <small class="error">Your PayPal account email is required.</small>
        </div>
        <div class="paypal-email-confirmation-field">
            <label>Confirm PayPal account email
                <input type="email" required data-equalto="paypal-email">
            </label>
            <small class="error">Your PayPal email account did not match.</small>
        </div>
        <div class="row bottom-rule">&nbsp;</div>
        <button type="submit" class="small-12">Continue</button>
    </form>
    <div class="row bottom-rule">&nbsp;</div>
    <div class="explainer">
        <p>Currently, all withdrawals from Kiva must be sent to a PayPal account, and cannot be transferred directly to a bank account. If you don't have a PayPal account, you can create one at <a href="https://www.paypal.com/">paypal.com</a>.</p>
        <p>Have questions about your withdrawal? Email us at <a href="mailto:contactus@kiva.org">contactus@kiva.org</a>.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="row bottom-rule">&nbsp;</div>
</div>

<div class="spacer" style="clear:both"></div>